<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />欸，<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" />。<delay40 />
我們偶爾也來聊聊<delay20 />
女孩子間的話題嘛！<anim id="Eh" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你是說女孩子間的<tag a="110" b="0" />話題嗎？</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />沒錯唷！<20_2 arg="3" /><delay40 />
像是流行時尚啦<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />還有戀愛的話題！<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯～<delay20 />是說<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，
你有喜歡的品牌<delay8 /><20_2 arg="4" />之類的嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不好意思，<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />。<delay40 />
我對流行時尚這些，<delay8 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />實在沒什麼研究<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這樣啊～<20_2 arg="3" /><delay8 />真無聊～<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那<delay8 /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像是最近關注的事之類的呢？<20_2 arg="4" /></message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果是這個話題，我也可以加入喔！<delay frames="60" />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我最近很關注<delay8 />
「蟑螂的可能性」這件事！<anim id="TakenAback" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><20_2 arg="8" /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大家都覺得蟑螂很討厭對吧！<anim id="Worried" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><20_3 arg="4" /><delay20 />
其實我也很怕蟑螂！！<delay20 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是<delay8 />仔細想想<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><20_2 arg="7" /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />蟑螂這種生物<delay8 />比我們還有恐龍
更早生存在這個世界上，<delay20 />
而且維持著繁榮的生態！<anim id="Shaking" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><20_2 arg="8" /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這也就是說，<delay20 />
<anim id="Worried" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />蟑螂是所有生物的<delay8 />
大前輩對吧？<pageBreak /><20_2 arg="7" /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我們應該尊敬牠，<delay8 />而不是討厭牠，<delay8 />
難道<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="TakenAback" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />不是這樣嗎！？<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然<delay20 />我是這麼想的，<anim id="Frantic" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay8 />
可是最後<delay8 />我還是得到討厭的東西
就是討厭這個結論<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />你覺得怎麼樣呢？<delay frames="60" /><anim id="Sighing" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />
我有成功加入女孩子的話題了嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果是這個話題，我也可以加入喔！<delay40 />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我最近很關注<delay20 />
「時間旅行是否可行」<delay8 /><anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />這件事！<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />因為我自己<20_3 arg="4" />
特別喜歡有時光機<delay20 /><20_2 arg="8" />
出現的故事！<anim id="Nodding" target="player" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />畢竟只要使用時光機，<delay8 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就能回到過去看恐龍，
<20_2 arg="7" />或是去看未來的自己不是嗎？<pageBreak /><20_3 arg="8" /><anim id="Sleepy" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果可以的話<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
我也好想體驗看看<delay8 />
時間旅行喔！
<anim id="Sleep" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，<delay20 /><20_2 arg="3" />冷靜想一想，
「現在」以外的時間，<anim id="Eh" target="player" targetSpec="" /><delay8 />
<20_2 arg="4" />真的存在嗎<tag a="110" b="0" />？<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然越想就越覺得<delay8 />
這個問題難以解答，<20_3 arg="7" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但我還是忍不住<anim id="TakenAback" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />會想像這種事呢！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你覺得怎麼樣呢？<20_2 arg="3" /><delay frames="60" />
<anim id="Worried" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />我有成功加入女孩子的話題了嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果是這個話題，我也可以加入喔！<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我最近很關注<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />「人魚是否真的存在？」<delay8 />這件事！<pageBreak /><20_2 arg="8" /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然<delay8 />常常有人說根本沒有人魚，<20_3 arg="4" />
那只是把海牛看錯了而已。<delay20 />
<20_2 arg="7" /><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Nodding" target="player" targetSpec="" /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />但我相信人魚一定是真實存在的！<pageBreak /><20_2 arg="6" /><anim id="Restless" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真希望有天我也能見到人魚，<delay20 />
<20_2 arg="5" />聽聽看人魚在海裡的生活方式，<delay8 />
還有人魚的歷史<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Sleepy" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />然後，<delay8 /><anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Nodding" target="player" targetSpec="" />我想把這些見聞寫成一本書，
感覺一定會很棒的！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你覺得怎麼樣呢？<anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="60" />
我有成功加入女孩子的話題了嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="SadSpiral" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我第一次聽到女孩子間，<delay8 /><anim id="QuestionMark" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />會聊這麼難的話題耶！<anim id="WrySmile" target="player" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />抱歉，我放棄。<delay20 /><anim id="QuestionMark" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />這些我真的聽不懂啦！<anim id="WrySmile" target="player" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我想說要送<delay8 />
<tag a="110" b="11" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />禮物，<delay20 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Nodding" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />可是找好久都找不到適合的～<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">雖然幫對方挑選禮物很開心，<delay20 /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是找不到適合的禮物，<delay8 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />的確會很煩惱呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 03 00 00 00 00 00">欸欸，<20_2 arg="3" /><tag a="110" b="4" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 /><20_2 arg="8" />
你覺得<delay8 /><20_3 arg="3" />好禮物應該要
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />怎樣才找得到～？</message>
	<message label="103_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">偷偷調查</message>
	<message label="103_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">直接問對方</message>
	<message label="103_c" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">送自己想要的東西</message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哇～！<delay40 /><20_3 arg="6" />感覺那樣<delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />很像女特務，<delay8 />
超～帥的嘛～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="105" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">你是說<20_2 arg="2" />女特務嗎<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感覺就像故事裡說的一樣，好棒喔！<delay40 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不介意的話，能不能也讓我一起幫忙呢？<anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="106" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這樣<20_2 arg="3" />超讚的～！<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那應該<delay20 /><anim id="Scheming" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要先準備
兩套一樣的<delay8 />特務裝對吧！</message>
	<message label="107" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="HappyDance" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />咦？<20_2 arg="4" /><delay40 />那不是反而會<delay8 />
更引人注目嗎<anim id="WrySmile" target="player" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="108" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">嗯～<20_3 arg="6" /><delay40 /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然那樣送禮物，對方一定會想要，<delay20 />
但這樣就一點都不驚喜了<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="109" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想到<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><20_2 arg="2" />一個好主意了！<delay40 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那就由我去問問<delay8 />
對方想要什麼東西吧！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><20_3 arg="5" />問完以後，<delay20 />我再跟<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />說
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />買什麼禮物好，<delay8 /><anim id="Aha" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />這個辦法怎麼樣呢？</message>
	<message label="110" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" /><20_2 arg="3" /><delay8 />這個辦法真聰明～！<delay frames="60" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那我就拜託你幫忙囉？<delay40 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一定要很～自然地<delay8 />問對方唷！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="111" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><20_2 arg="4" />要很～自然地問<delay20 />對吧！<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我知道了，<delay20 />為了回應
<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />的期待，<anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay8 />我會好好努力的！<delay8 /><anim id="Clapping" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="112" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_3 arg="6" />這樣好像<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也不錯唷～<delay40 />
最壞的情況<delay8 />頂多是對方不要，
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我還可以自己把禮物收下來！</message>
	<message label="113" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />畢竟，<20_2 arg="2" />想送禮物<delay8 />給對方的心意，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="player" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Nodding" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />才是最重要的呢！</message>
	<message label="114" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好！<20_2 arg="3" /><delay40 />那禮物就送
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我最推薦的偶像寫真集，<delay20 />
或是官方馬克杯好了～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="TakenAback" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="115" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯<20_2 arg="4" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
又有種<delay8 />送個更符合對方喜好的禮物
會比較好的感覺呢<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="201" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，<delay8 />
你之前借給我的詩集，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />真是超～讚的說～！<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />讓我有種「原來人家說的培養感性，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />就是像這樣啊～」的感覺！<delay40 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看完連我都想自己寫詩了唷！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="202" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />能夠幫上<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" /><20_2 arg="4" /><delay8 />
你的忙<delay20 />，真是太好了！<pageBreak /><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />聽你這麼一說<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我覺得從<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />的口頭禪中，<anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay8 />
好像都能感受到你的情緒呢！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="203" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦～！<20_2 arg="3" /><delay20 />真的嗎！？<delay frames="60" /><anim id="Nodding" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />
連我平常的口頭禪都變得很有詩意，<delay8 />
我的感性<delay8 />到底磨練到什麼程度啦？
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊，<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，<delay8 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />還是你想用用看我的口頭禪～？<anim id="Eh" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />借給你也完全OK唷！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="204" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的可以嗎？<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那事不宜遲，<delay8 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我馬上來用用看喔！<anim id="Nodding" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵，<delay20 />這麼一來，<delay8 />
我是不是也變得跟<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />一樣，<delay8 /><anim id="SmugFace" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />
充滿感性了呢？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
